          <div class="column is-half">
          <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">The system</h3>
          <p class="muted">Updates and changes to the certificates are automatically linked to QR codes, which are re-recorded (hashed) on the blockchain platform. This information corresponds to NEN's Certificate Registration System.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px;align-self:center;">
