          <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Hardcopy</h3>
          <p class="muted">Certificates are actually printed on badges and certificates that are used on the worksite. This means that the validity can be checked instantly by superiors and/or regulators. </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
        <div class="icon-container advantages column is-one-quarter" style="left:48px;height:280px;background-image: url('/assets/rocks/rock-3.svg')">
